---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service">
  <main class="flex-grow flex flex-col w-full bg-slate-950 py-20 px-6 sm:px-12">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto w-full">
      
      <header class="mb-12 border-b border-slate-800 pb-8">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-serif text-white mb-4">Terms of Service</h1>
        <p class="text-slate-400 font-light">Last Updated: March 24, 2026</p>
      </header>

      <section class="space-y-8 text-slate-300 leading-relaxed font-light text-sm sm:text-base">
        
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-serif text-white mb-3">1. Agreement to Terms</h2>
          <p>
            By accessing or using The Automated Solo (the "Site"), you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree with any part of these terms, you are prohibited from using the Site.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-serif text-white mb-3">2. Educational Purposes Only</h2>
          <p>
            All content, research, playbooks, and reviews provided by The Automated Solo are for informational and educational purposes only. Despite our focus on the legal industry, <strong>we are not providing legal, technical, or financial advice.</strong> You are solely responsible for ensuring that any tool, software, or workflow you choose to implement in your law firm complies with your local professional responsibility rules, bar association guidelines, and data protection laws.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-serif text-white mb-3">3. Affiliate and Financial Disclosure</h2>
          <p>
            The Automated Solo is a research laboratory that relies in part on affiliate commissions to fund our deep-dive testing. We may earn a commission when you click on links to partner products (such as AppSumo, PartnerStack, and individual SaaS tools) and make a purchase. This comes at absolutely no additional cost to you and does not compromise the independence of our reviews.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-serif text-white mb-3">4. Intellectual Property</h2>
          <p>
            The content, design, aesthetic, and structure of the Site, including but not limited to the Playbooks, methodologies, and original graphics, are owned by The Automated Solo. You may not reproduce, distribute, or repurpose our content without explicit written permission.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-serif text-white mb-3">5. Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
          <p>
            We extensively evaluate the software we feature, but software environments change rapidly. The site is provided on an "AS-IS" and "AS-AVAILABLE" basis. We make no representations or warranties about the fitness, reliability, or continued lifetime availability of any third-party tools reviewed on our platform.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-serif text-white mb-3">6. Limitations of Liability</h2>
          <p>
            In no event shall The Automated Solo or its operators be liable for any indirect, consequential, incidental, or strictly special damages arising from your use of the site or the software tools we review.
          </p>
        </div>

      </section>

    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>